            <p>Εἷς <expan>
                  <abbr>Θ</abbr><ex>εό</ex><abbr>ς</abbr>
               </expan> ὁ π<unclear>ά</unclear>
               <lb/>ντων <choice><sic>Δεσπ<lb/>ότες</sic><corr>Δεσπότης</corr></choice>. <choice><sic>Μ<unclear>ν</unclear>η<unclear>μ</unclear>ῖ<lb/>ον</sic><corr>Μνημεῖον</corr></choice>
                        Μ<unclear>α</unclear>τρώνη<lb/>ς Νόννα, ἀπο<lb/>θανούσης μετ<lb/>ὰ καλοῦ
                    ὀνόμ<lb/>ατος καὶ καλῆ<lb/>ς πίστεως ἐτῶν<lb/> κεʹ, ἐν <choice><sic>ἔτι</sic><corr>ἔτει</corr></choice> τοθʹ, ἐν<lb/>
               <choice><sic>μενὶ</sic><corr>μηνὶ</corr></choice> Δύστρου<lb/> ιγʹ, ἐν ἡμέρᾳ δʹ.<lb/>
               <choice><sic>Θάρσι,</sic><corr>Θάρσει</corr></choice>
               <choice><sic>οὐδὶς </sic><corr>οὐδείς</corr></choice>
               <choice><sic>ὀθ<lb/>ατος</sic><corr>ἀθάνατος</corr></choice>.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="zoor0241.translation" corresp="#zoor0241.transcription">
            <p> One (is) the God, the Lord of all. Monument of Matrona, (daughter) of Nonna(s),
                    who died having a good name and good faith (at the age) of 25 years, in (the)
                    year 379, on (the) 13th (day) of (the) month Dystros, on (the) 4th day
                    (Wednesday). Be of good cheer, no one (is) immortal.</p>
         </div>
